markets.title: Justin Bieber holds top ten spots on the Billboard Hot 100?
markets.subtitle: By Jul 26, 2025
markets.rules_primary: If Justin Bieber holds the top ten spots on the Billboard Hot 100 by Jul 26, 2025, then the market resolves to Yes.
